
Your request, mail, channel chat or tell was not very specific,
this is often a mistake newbies make, and this help file is to
help you communicate better over the system.

EXAMPLE OF A BAD COMMUNICATION: 
        "something is wrong with this thing"
EXAMPLE OF A GOOD COMMUNICATION:: 
        "in this room is an npc that dosnt fight"


The key to an effective and nospammy communication includes:
WHAT, HOW, WHY, WHEN, WHERE. Include them or be ignored.


